 and to make the best of our time at home.</p>"},{"id":"21647","title":"The Fall of Babylon, the Spread of Viruses, and the Rise of Nyctophobia","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/persons/_/50/50/holland_chris.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Chris Holland"}],"duration":3585.7,"recordingDate":"2020-03-14T11:00:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74902/2020/03/21647/20200314-1100-21647-211e37fc37ad4c01903d64e09f552006-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74904/2020/03/21647/20200314-1100-21647-211e37fc37ad4c01903d64e09f552006-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74905/2020/03/21647/20200314-1100-21647-211e37fc37ad4c01903d64e09f552006-16k.mp3"}],"description":""},{"id":"21645","title":"Ask Pastor Mark Live | Coronavirus Edition","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/persons/_/50/50/Finley_Mark.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Mark Finley"}],"duration":2435.2,"recordingDate":"2020-03-14T09:00:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74880/2020/03/21645/20200314-0900-21645-6468c687b166cf843b7e57133d4d5e26-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74881/2020/03/21645/20200314-0900-21645-6468c687b166cf843b7e57133d4d5e26-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/74882/2020/03/21645/20200314-0900-21645-6468c687b166cf843b7e57133d4d5e26-16k.mp3"}],"description":"<p>This is a special Coronavirus edition of Ask Pastor Mark Live. Pastor Mark will have a 20 minute Bible study on pestilence, Coronavirus and health prevention followed by a live question and answer session.</p>"},{"id":"21591","title":"The Time Is Near","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/persons/_/50/50/Kreuzer_Chad.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Chad Kreuzer"}],"duration":3227.8,"recordingDate":"2020-03-06T18:15:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audi